item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: iikrp
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

KIM KLASS

There is nothing I like more then the look on the special couples face when they see their wedding photos for the first time.  I am Kim, an award winning photographer from Somerset. When you hire me you can relax and trust me to capture your amazing day with breath taking photos. You are more then in good hands.

If you would like to see examples of my photo’s in person and have a chat contact me on 019324 23423 or use our contact form. I would love to hear from you.

A PERSONALISED SERVICE.

You can completely dictate how I photograph your day or leave it to me. I have plenty of experience with all types, sizes and locations so can work with any scenario to make sure the end result is always something that goes above your expectations of me. My aim is to make you enjoy your day as much as possible. [/text][/column][column size="col-md-6"][text padding_bottom="30px"]

CAPTURING YOUR DAY, YOUR WAY.

Whether you want candid, staged or a bit of both I can make your photos reflect your day and how you'd like to remember it. Working alongside your vision my aim is to make my photos act as the perfect memory. We couldn't be happier with Kim's photo's. She listened to how we wanted the day captured and blended into the wedding so well. In short an absolute professional and we have some stunning memories thanks to her.

We loved the documentary style of the photos and were amazed by some of the candid shots Kim managed to get without anyone noticing her! It made re-living the day all the more special to see things we didn't on the day through Kim's photos. Thank you so much for everything.
